    Note over TestSuite, S3: Flow 1: PyTorchJob Distributed Training (KFTO)

    TestSuite->>K8sAPI: Create PyTorchJob CR + LocalQueue<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI->>Kueue: Workload admission
    Kueue-->>K8sAPI: Workload admitted
    K8sAPI->>TrainingOp: PyTorchJob event
    TrainingOp->>K8sAPI: Create Master & Worker Pods<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Master->>Worker: Distributed training (c10d)<br/>29500/TCP gRPC plaintext
    Master->>S3: Save model checkpoint<br/>443/TCP HTTPS AWS IAM
    S3-->>Master: Upload confirmed
    TestSuite->>K8sAPI: Poll PyTorchJob status
    K8sAPI-->>TestSuite: Job completed

    Note over TestSuite, S3: Flow 2: Ray Cluster MNIST Training

    TestSuite->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI->>KubeRay: RayCluster event
    KubeRay->>K8sAPI: Create Head & Worker Pods<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    RayHead->>RayWorker: GCS connection<br/>6379/TCP gRPC plaintext
    TestSuite->>K8sAPI: Create Route for Ray Dashboard
    TestSuite->>RayDash: Submit RayJob<br/>443/TCP HTTPS edge TLS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    RayDash->>RayHead: Forward job<br/>8265/TCP HTTP plaintext
    RayHead->>RayWorker: Distribute MNIST training tasks
    RayHead-->>RayDash: Job result
    RayDash-->>TestSuite: Job completed

    Note over TestSuite, S3: Flow 3: Notebook-driven Ray Job

    TestSuite->>K8sAPI: Create Notebook CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI->>NotebookCtrl: Notebook event
    NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Notebook Pod<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    NotebookPod->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: User Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>KubeRay: RayCluster event
    KubeRay->>K8sAPI: Create Ray Pods
    NotebookPod->>RayHead: Submit job via Ray Dashboard<br/>8265/TCP HTTP plaintext
    RayHead-->>NotebookPod: Job result
